  "description": "A component that enhances PostgreSQL with vector similarity search \ncapabilities through the pgvector extension. It allows for storing and querying of \nhigh-dimensional vectors directly within your existing PostgreSQL database. \nThis component is ideal for building AI-powered applications that require semantic search, \nrecommendation engines, and other similarity-based features without the need \nfor a separate, specialized vector database.",
